==English==
===Etymology===
Likely an overzealous typo of [[OMG]], resulting from the proximity of [[z]] to the shift key.  

==={{initialism}}===
'''ZOMG'''

#(''Internet slang'') ''Zounds, Oh My God/Gosh/Goodness''; variants include [[OMFG]], ''Oh My Freaking/Fucking God/Gosh'', and [[OMG]],  ''Oh My God/Gosh/Goodness".

